\begin_layout Standard
The Ashbian cybernetic interpretation adds an essential twist: the values
 and structure of the feedback loop are not setup by a designer but rather
 determined by the organism itself through a random walk of possible parameter:
 in the beginning the connection between the motor action (the organism
\begin_inset Quotes ers
